      "review_summary": "The PR adds bounded retry handling for Feishu `230020` send rate-limit errors in `requestFeishuApi`, routes text/card replies through that helper, and adds retry/concurrency tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +51, Tests +409. Total +460 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Current main has source-reproducible one-shot Feishu message delivery paths, and the PR body supplies live after-fix Feishu terminal proof for direct and reply sends; I did not run local tests because this is a read-only review.",
