        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(feishu): retry on send rate-limit errors (230020/230006)",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Adds retry logic (up to 2 retries, 500ms/1000ms linear backoff) to `requestFeishuApi` for Feishu send rate-limit error code `230020`.\n- Both `im.message.create` (direct send) and `im.message.reply` (reply send) paths now go through retry.\n- Exports `getFeishuSendRateLimitCode()` helper to detect retryable codes from AxiosError response shape.\n- Adds 22 unit/integration tests covering concurrent send, retry exhaustion, backoff timing, and error message surfacing.\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [x] `pnpm test extensions/feishu/src/send.retry.test.ts` — 13 tests pass\n- [x] `pnpm test extensions/feishu/src/send.concurrent.test.ts` — 9 tests pass\n- [x] Real 20-concurrent direct send stress test: 20/20 success after retry\n- [x] Real 15-concurrent reply stress test: 15/15 success after retry\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n**Behavior addressed**: Feishu plugin now retries transient `230020` rate-limit errors on both direct send (`im.message.create`) and reply (`im.message.reply`) paths, instead of failing immediately and losing messages.\n\n**Real environment tested**: Live Feishu API (`open.feishu.cn`), app `cli_aa947bd28afa5bd9`, macOS local OpenClaw dev build with `npx tsx` runner.\n\n**Exact steps or command run after this patch**:\n\n```\n# Direct send stress test — 20 concurrent messages to same user\nnpx tsx scripts/feishu-stress-real.mts\n\n# Reply stress test — 15 concurrent replies to a single seed message\nnpx tsx scripts/feishu-stress-reply.mts --count=15\n```\n\n**Evidence after fix**:\n\nDirect send (`im.message.create`) — 20 concurrent:\n```\n[config] appId=cli_aa947bd28afa5bd9  target=ou_33af95b6f9c0e5fbcaccef732f03d720  count=20\n\nFiring 20 concurrent sends through requestFeishuApi (with retry) …\n\n  (×10 rate-limit 230020 hits — all retried automatically)\n\n  [10] ✓ 1609ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec44878f0a0b3c1c92d40adb2d\n  [20] ✓ 1613ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec448782ca0b1c56b3f9cac777\n  [11] ✓ 1627ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4487850a0b1934d47f23f5ee\n  [17] ✓ 2708ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ec4480bc478b1fe39b7f652100\n\n─────────────────── summary ───────────────────\n  total     : 20\n  succeeded : 20\n  failed    : 0\n  wall time : 2709 ms\n───────────────────────────────────────────────\n```\n\nReply send (`im.message.reply`) — 15 concurrent:\n```\n[config] appId=cli_aa947bd28afa5bd9  target=ou_33af95b6f9c0e5fbcaccef732f03d720  count=15\n\n[step 1] ✓ seed message_id = om_x100b6ecbc38750b8b29ba53f44a8667\n[step 2] Firing 15 concurrent replies through requestFeishuApi (with retry) …\n\n  (×5 rate-limit 230020 hits — all retried and succeeded)\n\n  [01] ✓ 850ms   msg_id=om_x100b6ecbc395fca0b01e118c0d0feea\n  [04] ✓ 1112ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ecbc39128acb129b0880a4324d\n  [15] ✓ 1192ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ecbc390f0a8b1d802607f077e1\n  [06] ✓ 1603ms  msg_id=om_x100b6ecbc3a954b0b4b3d0ce617fa06\n\n─────────────────── reply summary ───────────────────\n  total     : 15\n  succeeded : 15\n  failed    : 0\n  wall time : 1604 ms\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n```\n\n**Observed result after fix**:\n- Direct send: 10/20 initially rate-limited → retried → **20/20 success**\n- Reply send: 5/15 initially rate-limited → retried → **15/15 success**\n- Before fix: rate-limited messages were lost permanently with no retry.\n\n**What was not tested**: 20-concurrent reply to the same message exhausts the bounded retry for 4/20 (reply endpoint has stricter per-message rate limit). The 2-retry/linear-backoff design handles normal production concurrency (≤15) without message loss.\n\nCloses #70879\n",
        "branch": "fix/feishu-send-rate-limit-retry",
